  "id": "RAW_3a2ea0",
  "title": "苹果提出原生多模态 Scaling Law！早融合+MoE，性能飙升秘密武器",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652591609&idx=3&sn=d9aaec885ee668c22058d44a04132989&subscene=0",
  "date": "2025-05-05 04:58:00",
  "author": "新智元",
  "siteName": "新智元",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\">\n        <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/590120f8-c65f-497f-a9b4-c0607db3c300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb1wbMVjW5XBeWsmGMhbLXedthSryINtDPtms4CYAF6f6ibGfjAW6esRdicJRl03gFo4dIfJubtebsMw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" data-imgfileid=\"505102211\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/590120f8-c65f-497f-a9b4-c0607db3c300/public\"></span>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\">\n   <span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：英智</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">研究揭示早融合架构在低计算预算下表现更优，训练效率更高。混合专家（MoE）技术让模型动态适应不同模态，显著提升性能，堪称多模态模型的秘密武器。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如今，打造强大的多模态模型是AI领域的重要目标。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一种常用方法是把单独预训练好的模型组合起来，比如把训练好的视觉编码器连接到LLM的输入层，再进行多模态训练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，单模态预训练可能会带来一些偏差，影响模型对不同模态之间相互依赖关系的学习。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">且每个单模态组件都有自己的超参数、预训练数据和缩放属性，给系统扩展增加了不少难度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究人员把希望寄托在了原生多模态模型（NMM）上，NMM是在所有模态上同时从头开始训练的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种全新的训练方式能不能突破现有的困境，让模型性能更上一层楼呢？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">来自法国索邦大学、苹果的研究人员开展了原生多模态Scaling Laws的研究，表明早融合优于后融合，多模态MoE好于密集模型。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4bdb64bb-00d3-43d4-5298-4f031c650500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4435173299101412\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1558\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1558\" data-height=\"691\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"249\" data-imgfileid=\"505102238\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4bdb64bb-00d3-43d4-5298-4f031c650500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">论文链接：https://arxiv.org/abs/2504.07951</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究表明，后融合架构相较于不依赖图像编码器的早融合架构，并没有固有优势。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">早融合架构在参数数量较少时，性能更强，训练效率更高，部署起来也更容易。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">引入混合专家（MoE）技术，能让模型学到特定模态的权重，进而大幅提升性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究成果总结如下：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">原生早融合与后融合性能相当</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：从零开始训练的早融合模型与后融合模型性能相当，在计算预算较低时，早融合模型略有优势。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ab8bf406-4f28-46ef-87c2-8e20eefc5600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.36660143509458576\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1533\" data-width=\"1533\" data-height=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"505102236\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ab8bf406-4f28-46ef-87c2-8e20eefc5600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此外，Scaling Law研究表明，随着计算预算的增加，早融合和后融合的计算最优模型性能相似（图1-左）。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/79306c87-0570-4fd7-7a88-1ef0cb09d800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5861618798955613\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1532\" data-width=\"1532\" data-height=\"898\" data-imgfileid=\"505102240\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/79306c87-0570-4fd7-7a88-1ef0cb09d800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">原生多模态模型（NMM）Scaling Law与LLM相似</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：原生多模态模型的扩展规律与纯文本LLM相似，扩展指数因目标数据类型和训练混合比例略有变化。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6798a24-4208-4165-0204-989ce2ccd000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.37438423645320196\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1624\" data-width=\"1624\" data-height=\"608\" data-imgfileid=\"505102239\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6798a24-4208-4165-0204-989ce2ccd000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">后融合需要更多参数</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：与早融合相比，计算最优的后融合模型需要更高的参数-数据比（图1-右）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">稀疏性显著提升早融合NMM性能</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：在相同推理成本下，稀疏NMM相较于密集模型有显著改进。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ddb523fd-4046-4e52-64e4-ef0589117400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8480603448275862\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"928\" data-width=\"928\" data-height=\"787\" data-imgfileid=\"505102237\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ddb523fd-4046-4e52-64e4-ef0589117400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此外，稀疏训练的模型会隐式学习模态特定权重。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">随着计算预算增加，计算最优模型更依赖于增加训练token数量，而非活跃参数数量（图1-右）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于稀疏NMM，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模态无关路由优于模态感知路由</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：在稀疏专家混合模型中，使用模态无关路由训练的性能始终优于采用模态感知路由的模型。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/66fdb0ec-433c-496e-99a7-166030639d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8635875402792696\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"931\" data-width=\"931\" data-height=\"804\" data-imgfileid=\"505102245\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/66fdb0ec-433c-496e-99a7-166030639d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">原生多模态Scaling Law</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为深入了解原生多模态模型的性能表现，研究人员引入了Scaling Law的概念。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">通过计算模型的浮点运算次数（FLOPs）来衡量计算量的大小，并且假设模型最终的损失和模型的大小（用参数数量N来表示）以及训练token的数量（D）之间存在一种幂律关系：</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3691ea20-3cea-423d-54d5-2d4917ab3e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3237822349570201\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"698\" style=\"width:171px;height:55px;\" data-width=\"698\" data-height=\"226\" data-imgfileid=\"505102242\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3691ea20-3cea-423d-54d5-2d4917ab3e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">E代表在数据集上可达到的最低损失，</span><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1575e932-f1ad-4da1-77f9-4da8b77bf200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2911392405063291\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"158\" style=\"width:24px;height:31px;\" data-width=\"158\" data-height=\"204\" data-imgfileid=\"505102241\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1575e932-f1ad-4da1-77f9-4da8b77bf200/public\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">表示增加模型参数数量对损失的影响，一般来说，模型参数越多，损失就会越低，α是控制这种变化速度的，</span><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2f73d245-8b4d-481d-6bb2-a6027a426d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.361904761904762\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"210\" style=\"width:20px;height:27px;\" data-width=\"210\" data-height=\"286\" data-imgfileid=\"505102243\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2f73d245-8b4d-481d-6bb2-a6027a426d00/public\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">体现了增加训练token数量带来的好处，β决定了其增长速度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">同时，研究人员还发现计算预算（FLOPs）和N、D之间存在线性关系</span><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8e8ca619-c273-46b9-4f52-0facf5d5f300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2517361111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"576\" style=\"width:80px;height:20px;\" data-width=\"576\" data-height=\"145\" data-imgfileid=\"505102244\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8e8ca619-c273-46b9-4f52-0facf5d5f300/public\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">早融合和后融合模型的Scaling Law。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">图2（左）呈现了早融合的NMM在多模态交织、图像-描述以及文本这三类数据集上的平均最终损失。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b3f5df27-890d-4e57-1c9e-cbd4d05b7f00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47448641484426773\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1509\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1509\" data-height=\"716\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"267\" data-imgfileid=\"505102251\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b3f5df27-890d-4e57-1c9e-cbd4d05b7f00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可以看到，其最低损失的变化趋势遵循着与浮点运算次数（FLOPs）相关的幂律关系。通过对这一规律进行拟合，得到表达式</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5b1df62f-a32e-4a5d-068a-d0a78872f600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2208904109589041\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"584\" style=\"width: 94px;height: 21px;\" data-width=\"584\" data-height=\"129\" data-imgfileid=\"505102247\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5b1df62f-a32e-4a5d-068a-d0a78872f600/public\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">反映出随着计算量的增加，模型性能提升的速度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在分析不同数据类型（如图像字幕、交错、文本）时，观察到指数有所不同。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/da32c0f8-f5eb-4b14-645c-d4bb63b87900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.36622390891840606\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1581\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1581\" data-height=\"579\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"206\" data-imgfileid=\"505102250\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/da32c0f8-f5eb-4b14-645c-d4bb63b87900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与交错文档相比，模型在图像字幕数据上实现了更高的性能提升速率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">图2（右）后融合模型中，观察到损失Scaling指数与早融合几乎相同。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究人员采用了457个具有不同架构和训练混合方式的训练模型，模型的参数量从0.3B到4B。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们还调整了训练token的数量，同时改变训练数据的混合方式，以此来全面探究各种因素对模型性能的影响。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究人员采用了自回归Transformer架构，搭配SwiGLU前馈网络和QK-Norm技术，还使用了像bfloat16、全分片数据并行（FSDP）、激活检查点和梯度累积等多种优化方法，让训练更高效。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8cdb12e-23c7-4a3c-9240-c4c752487800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8cdb12e-23c7-4a3c-9240-c4c752487800/public\"></span></strong></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">早融合优势尽显</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在低计算预算（模型规模较小）的情况下，早融合模型略胜一筹。</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">随着计算预算的增加，虽然两种模型的性能逐渐接近，但早融合模型在训练效率上具有明显优势。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/caac6286-c39d-4143-1949-de162b9de800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5435356200527705\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1516\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1516\" data-height=\"824\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"305\" data-imgfileid=\"505102256\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/caac6286-c39d-4143-1949-de162b9de800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对比NMM和仅基于文本的LLM（如GPT-3、Chinchilla）的Scaling Law系数，会发现它们处于相似范围。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">早融合与后融合NMM的计算最优权衡。虽然后融合和早融合模型随着FLOPs增加，损失降低的速度相近。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在缩放FLOPs时，早融合模型的参数数量明显更少，这对降低推理成本很关键，部署后也能降低服务成本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在计算资源相同的情况下，早融合模型不仅占用的内存更少，训练速度也更快。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当计算量增大时，这种优势愈发显著。这说明早融合在保持相当的大规模训练时性能时，还具备超高的训练效率。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f132d083-a99e-4fa2-1fd6-bbf10762b700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9396325459317585\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"762\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"762\" data-height=\"716\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"528\" data-imgfileid=\"505102252\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f132d083-a99e-4fa2-1fd6-bbf10762b700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">值得注意，在相同的FLOPs下，与早融合模型相比，后融合模型具有更高的参数量和有效深度。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8cdb12e-23c7-4a3c-9240-c4c752487800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8cdb12e-23c7-4a3c-9240-c4c752487800/public\"></span></strong></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">不同数据混合的Scaling Law</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">图4表明不同的数据混合方式在模型训练中呈现出相似的缩放趋势，不过它们的缩放系数存在差异（表4）。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5a48e9b3-bffa-4704-516b-5ec6f338a800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4470198675496689\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1510\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1510\" data-height=\"675\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"251\" data-imgfileid=\"505102255\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5a48e9b3-bffa-4704-516b-5ec6f338a800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e7aebfcd-7576-457e-a618-b2a1c15cb900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24848891873740767\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1489\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1489\" data-height=\"370\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"139\" data-imgfileid=\"505102253\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e7aebfcd-7576-457e-a618-b2a1c15cb900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有趣的是，增加图像字幕数据的比例（混合方式1和2）会导致a值降低和b值升高，而增加交错和文本数据的比例（混合方式3和4）会产生相反的效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">图像说明数据中，图像token占比高于文本token。因此，提高图像说明数据的比例会增加图像token数量，而增加多模态交织数据或文本数据的比例则会提升文本token数量。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这表明，当图像token占主导时，训练时间越长，损失下降越快，增加模型规模会进一步加速这一过程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于固定的模型大小，增加纯文本和交错数据的比例有利于早融合模型。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3723fc6e-9133-45c1-88ee-69c30db97600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0146082337317397\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"753\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"753\" data-height=\"764\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"570\" data-imgfileid=\"505102254\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3723fc6e-9133-45c1-88ee-69c30db97600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8cdb12e-23c7-4a3c-9240-c4c752487800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8cdb12e-23c7-4a3c-9240-c4c752487800/public\"></span></strong></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">原生多模态预训练与LLM的持续训练</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对比两种训练方式：一种是从头开始进行原生训练，另一种是先用预训练的LLM进行初始化，再持续训练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实验用的初始模型是DCLM-1B，它在超过2T个token的数据上完成了训练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">随着训练时间的延长，NMM和经过初始化的模型之间的差距会逐渐缩小。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9e11e21e-b417-4b43-b51c-f1ffc957e000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3756720430107527\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1488\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1488\" data-height=\"559\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"211\" data-imgfileid=\"505102258\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9e11e21e-b417-4b43-b51c-f1ffc957e000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">具体来说，在图像字幕数据上，模型需要不到100B个多模态token就能达到可比的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，在交错和文本数据上，模型可能需要更长的训练时间（多达1T token）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">考虑到预训练的成本，为了实现相同的性能，原生多模态训练可能是更有效的方法。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8cdb12e-23c7-4a3c-9240-c4c752487800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8cdb12e-23c7-4a3c-9240-c4c752487800/public\"></span></strong></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">多模态专业化：MoE的妙用</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">早融合模型在很多方面表现出色，但多模态数据的异构性仍然是一个挑战。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了让模型更好地处理这种异构数据，研究人员引入了专家混合（MoE）技术。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">MoE技术允许模型在不同模态之间动态分配专门的参数，以更好地适应多模态数据的特点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实验结果显示，在相同推理成本下，MoE模型的表现明显好于密集模型，尤其是在模型较小时，优势更为明显。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这说明MoE架构在处理异构数据时更高效，还能针对不同模态进行专门处理。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c39fbf9e-47f7-4288-3706-9f5a7d67cc00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8635851183765502\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"887\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"887\" data-height=\"766\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"485\" data-imgfileid=\"505102259\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c39fbf9e-47f7-4288-3706-9f5a7d67cc00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了验证前面通过验证损失得到的结论在实际应用中的有效性，研究人员在下游任务上进行了评估。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们在LLaVA混合数据上进行了多模态指令调整阶段（SFT），并在多个视觉问答（VQA）和图像字幕任务中测试了模型的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8c4958f5-c17d-4dfe-f454-8dfb51db6800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.23019634394041977\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1477\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1477\" data-height=\"340\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"130\" data-imgfileid=\"505102257\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8c4958f5-c17d-4dfe-f454-8dfb51db6800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">结果再次证实了之前的发现：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">早融合模型优于后融合模型，采用MoE的模型优于密集模型</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过，由于实验中的模型相对较小（1.5B），并且是从头开始训练并在小数据集上微调，总体分数与当前最先进的模型还有一定差距。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但这也为后续的研究指明了方向，即通过进一步优化模型规模、训练数据和微调策略，有望提升模型在实际任务中的表现。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://www.alphaxiv.org/overview/2504.07951</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5c01fefd-3c28-4443-6252-85fee59fbb00/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5796296296296296\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"326\" data-imgfileid=\"505099958\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5c01fefd-3c28-4443-6252-85fee59fbb00/public\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "苹果提出原生多模态模型 Scaling Law，揭示早融合和 MoE 的优势，为多模态模型设计提供指导。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "苹果提出原生多模态模型 Scaling Law，揭示早融合和 MoE 的优势，为多模态模型设计提供指导。",
  "summary": "本文研究了苹果公司提出的原生多模态模型（NMM）的 Scaling Law，通过大量实验，分析了不同架构和训练方式对模型性能的影响，揭示了其对于理解和优化多模态模型的重要性。研究表明，在低计算预算下，早融合架构优于后融合架构，且训练效率更高。通过引入混合专家（MoE）技术，模型能够学习特定模态的权重，从而显著提升性能。实验结果表明，早融合模型和采用 MoE 的模型在视觉问答和图像字幕任务中表现更优。此外，文章还探讨了不同数据混合方式对模型性能的影响，以及原生多模态预训练与 LLM 持续训练的对比。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "通过 Scaling Law 研究，发现早融合架构在低计算预算下性能更优，训练效率更高",
      "explanation": "与后融合架构相比，早融合架构在参数数量较少时表现更强，且更易于部署，降低了推理成本。"
    },
    {
      "point": "MoE 技术通过动态分配参数，显著提升多模态模型性能",
      "explanation": "混合专家技术允许模型在不同模态之间动态分配专门的参数，从而更好地适应多模态数据的特点，提升性能。"
    },
    {
      "point": "数据混合方式影响模型性能，图像 token 占比高时训练更快",
      "explanation": "增加图像字幕数据的比例会导致训练时间越长，损失下降越快，增加模型规模会进一步加速这一过程。"
    }
  ],
